<li id="cite_note-86"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-86">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Ellis, Peter Berresford. 1985. <i>The Celtic Revolution: A Study in Anti-imperialism</i>. Talybont: Y Lolfa.</span>
